## 9. Import Run Results (POST /import/run-results)

Accepts a CSV file upload matching the run_results table schema.
Required columns: run_id, question_id, prompt_version, run_timestamp,
overall_passed, section_1_passed through section_7_passed,
root_failure_section, root_failure_mode, latency_ms, tokens_used.

On import:
1. Validate all question_ids exist in the questions table.
   Reject rows where question_id not found.
2. Reject duplicate (run_id, question_id) pairs.
3. Insert valid rows.
4. Show flash message: "Imported N rows from run RUN-ID. Rejected M rows."
5. Redirect to /dashboard.

