## 11. Startup Behaviour

On startup (first run):
1. Create the SQLite database if it does not exist.
2. Create all tables.
3. Seed the agents table with release_agent and document_agent if empty.
4. Do not seed questions — those are authored by the user.

Run command:
```bash
uv run uvicorn regression.main:app --reload --port 8080
```

URL: http://localhost:8080

